Definition: make a logical or causal connection
Example: I cannot connect these two pieces of evidence in my mind; colligate these facts; I cannot relate these events at all
Synonyms: adj, all, associative, associable, associatory, noun, state, association, cognition, dissociate, tie_in, relate, Tops, relation, link, linkage, colligate, colligation, link_up, connect, conjunctive, connective, connection, connexion, think, make, a, logical, or, causal, I, cannot, these, two, pieces, of, evidence, in, my, mind, facts, events, at
